10. Short glossary in easy words\par
- CI/CD: Tools that build and give out new versions automatically.\par
- Docker: A tool to package apps so they run the same on many machines.\par
- Image: A package for Docker.\par
- Container: A running instance of an image.\par
- Ansible: A tool that runs steps on other machines.\par
- Playbook: A file that says what Ansible should do.\par
- SSH key: A secret that lets one machine log in to another without a password.\par
